data.title: Crawford Library of the Health Sciences-Rockford
data.text:
The Crawford Library of the Health Sciences-Rockford serves students, faculty and residents at the College of Medicine, College of Nursing, College of Pharmacy, National Center for Rural Health Professions and Medical Biotechnology Program at Rockford.

Please see also general contact info for the UIC Library (not just the Library of the Health Sciences).
